    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've already talked to people. they just say the same stuff, like \"it gets better\" or \"give it time.\" but time doesn't change the fact that i failed. it just means more time spent feeling like this. i don't want to \"navigate\" the pain, i just want it to stop. it feels like i'm just walking in circles. wouldn't it be more logical to just... stop walking?",
